Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=16}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:53.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.43,0:01:56.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que você está aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:58.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como você embarcou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:01.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que, afinal...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.27,0:02:02.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como vai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:05.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sou o Sogeking, Rei dos Atiradores.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:08.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Resumindo,\Nvim te resgatar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:10.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Narigudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.28,0:02:11.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não sou só eu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:17.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Sr. Sanji e um brutamontes chamado Franky estão\Nem batalha neste trem neste momento.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:20.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso me deu a chance de vir até aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:21.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Além disso, o Sr. Luffy e os outros
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:25.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,estão nos perseguindo neste mesmo trilho\Na bordo de outro Sea Train...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:28.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aparentemente, estão trazendo bastante aliados.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:35.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,No caminho até aqui, espiei\Npelas janelas por dentro.
Comment: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:33.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,On my way here earlier,
Comment: 0,0:02:34.01,0:02:35.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I peeked inside of the train\Nthrough the windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.93,0:02:39.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Francamente, a equipe de quatro no\Nvagão atrás de nós é perigosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:45.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seria melhor se eu conseguisse tirá-la daqui\Nantes do Sr. Sanji enfrentá-los.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:53.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora, vamos escapar...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:55.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,juntos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:03.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que houve?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:05.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não precisa se preocupar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:07.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estou preparado.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:10.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esses octoshoes são pra você.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:13.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Use nos mãos e nos pés
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:16.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,pra que possamos sair pela janela\Ne nos agarrar ao Sea Train.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:18.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora, coloque-os antes que percebam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:19.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:20.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Espere"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:23.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como isso pode estar acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:28.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Achei que tinha dito adeus claramente a todos vocês.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.23,0:03:30.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nunca vou voltar para os Chapéus de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:40.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles sabem por que você\Ninsiste tanto nisso.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:44.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ouvi que o tal do Gelo\Nno estaleiro esclareceu tudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:48.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então ele sobreviveu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:50.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:52.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mesmo assim...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:54.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não vou voltar pra vocês...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:57.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chega disso!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:59.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você ainda não entende?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:01.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles não são tão fracos que\Nvocê precisa se preocupar com eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:07.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles realmente queriam que você tivesse\Nconversado antes de aceitar um acordo tão estúpido!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:11.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você acha mesmo que eles ficariam felizes em estar vivos
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:13.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,sabendo que a amiga deles deu a vida por eles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:16.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora que sabem por que você os deixou,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:21.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,eles vão te seguir até as profundezas do inferno\Ne derrubar seus inimigos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:25.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você ainda não entende que tipo de homem o Luffy é!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:29.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São vocês que não entendem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:32.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não tenho a menor vontade de ser resgatada!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:34.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês não podem simplesmente fazer o que querem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:37.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que disse, sua–
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:41.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que é todo esse barulho,\NNico Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que houve?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:52.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora que estamos nos aproximando de Enies Lobby,\Né difícil até pra {\i1}você{\i0} manter a calma?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:55.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chore sobre seu destino o quanto quiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:59.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não vai fazer nada pra salvar sua vida.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:00.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não é nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:05.24,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,O que foi aquilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:06.58,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Muito suspeito...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:11.37,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Além disso, ela parece diferente de alguma forma...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:15.00,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,É só minha imaginação?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não é nada...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:22.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,então por favor me deixem em paz.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:24.10,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Que droga é essa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:27.18,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que essa mulher está enrolando?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:33.98,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Um coelho...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:41.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bem-vindos ao mundo do ramen {\i1}kenpo{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:44.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que tipo de power-up...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:46.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora, agora, agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:48.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tome isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:50.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Ramen Kenpo:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:53.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Pork Bone Spank!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:03.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso não é só uma versão maior\Ndo mesmo soco inútil?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:07.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora, agora, agora! Mais um!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:14.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Estou preso!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.53,0:06:23.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora, agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:33.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora, agora, agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:34.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seu idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:37.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Está pasmo com meu ramen {\i1}kenpo{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:42.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você está ridículo com sua perna\Ne braço enterrados no macarrão!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:48.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem você pensa que é,\Nme batendo daquele jeito antes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:58.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Está sério ficando tonto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:04.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tentou me deixar zonzo\Ncom suas sobrancelhas de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:07.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não vou deixar passar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:15.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.79,0:07:18.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não consigo revidar assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:25.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Noodle Soul Press!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:33.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estou só começando!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:35.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mais uma porção!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E mais uma!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:38.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E mais uma!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:39.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E mais uma!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:41.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E mais uma!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:44.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,61)}Toma isso, e isso, e isso,\Ne isso, e isso, e isso, e isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:53.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Finalmente saíram.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora, agora, agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:08:01.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não está me subestimando, seu idiota?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:05.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Este é o maluco, maluco ramen {\i1}kenpo{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:09.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se eu atacar, fico enterrado no ramen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:13.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Acho que não posso tocar no macarrão.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:16.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora, vou continuar atacando!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:20.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Ramen-Gyoza Combo:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:23.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Clapping!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:30.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então só tem um lugar pra mirar, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:36.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Éscalope!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:41.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Ramen Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.93,0:08:52.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora, agora, agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:55.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não tenho ponto cego!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:09:00.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pelo que vi, seu estilo de luta\Né feito de chutes, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:03.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você fica indefeso sem seus chutes, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:06.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora, agora, agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não adianta! Não adianta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:11.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não importa o que você faça,\Nvai acabar enterrado na minha roupa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:16.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lá vai! Tente desviar dessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:19.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Ramen Kenpo:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:21.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Multi-Noodle Spank!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:44.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fedelini: uma massa de 1,4 milímetros...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:47.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Truque de mãos...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:51.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você cortou meus punhos de macarrão em pedaços!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:59.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mãos e facas de cozinha são sagradas pros cozinheiros.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:02.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então é minha política não usá-las em batalha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:06.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas se isso é uma cozinha...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:10.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,e meu inimigo é feito de comida,\Naí é outra história.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:15.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é mais problemático do que eu pensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:19.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Thousand-Noodle Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tentando parecer legal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:28.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que atrevido!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:32.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um amador como você que nem sabe\Ncozinhar não deveria segurar facas de cozinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:37.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Elas são diferentes das facas\Nque delinquentes usam!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:40.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Perdão pelo atrevimento.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:43.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aceite isso como um pedido de desculpas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:48.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Permita-me mostrar...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:53.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,como um cozinheiro de primeira...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:56.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,maneja magistralmente suas facas de cozinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:03.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:08.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Strong Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:10.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Paper Art.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:15.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Tempest Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:29.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Fresh Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:30.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:35.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê...?! Qual é a dele?!\NEle simplesmente pulou do trem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Moon Walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:44.23,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Como ele voltou no ar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.23,0:11:45.85,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Não entendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:48.56,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que não consigo cortá-lo com o Tempest Kick?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:52.02,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Tem algo estranho no corpo dele!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:54.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:55.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,...diabos...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:04.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\pos(414,1053)}...é você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:04.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1374,1053)}...é você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:11.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Já estamos perto do {\i1}Bashing Tom{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:12.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É "{\i1}Puffing{\i0}"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:15.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy! Fique dentro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:18.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você acabou de trocar de roupa, mas já\Nestá encharcado de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:19.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá tudo bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:20.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu gosto de ficar aqui em cima!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:21.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ai, ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:25.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.31,0:12:27.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Three-Hundred-Pound...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:28.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}– ...Cannon!\N– ...Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.44,0:12:29.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Boom!\N– Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:30.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Splash!\N– Splash!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:32.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Ahh! É isso! Laguna!\N– Ahh! É isso! Laguna!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:35.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não é hora de brincadeira!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.99,0:12:37.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Estamos entediados.\N– Estamos entediados.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:41.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vão polir as armas\Nou algo assim, seus idiotas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:44.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, é...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:48.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu falo com esses caras depois, então...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:52.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:55.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estou vendo um trem lá na frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:00.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Deve ser o {\i1}Puffing Tom{\i0}!\N– Deve ser o {\i1}Puffing Tom{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:04.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não é cedo demais?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:09.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:11.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que vai ser de nós?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:14.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não tem motor neste vagão.\NSó podemos esperar por resgate.
Comment: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:12.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,There's no engine on this car.
Comment: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:14.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We have no choice but to wait to be rescued.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:16.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau! Estamos balançando!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:20.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas quais são as chances de resgate\Nnuma tempestade dessas?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:23.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, pessoal. Tem algo\Nvindo por trás!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.12,0:13:23.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sério?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:24.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deve ser um navio de resgate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:27.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, parece que...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:29.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,está vindo pelos trilhos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.21,0:13:31.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:34.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Só existe um Sea Train no mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:38.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Além disso, nada poderia ter saído\Nde Water 7 depois daquela última partida.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:41.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:47.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,o que diabos está vindo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:53.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, aquilo é um Sea Train, mas são\Nsó vagões sem locomotiva!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:55.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Está bloqueando o trilho!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:56.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:57.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:00.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso quer dizer que foram desconectados?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:04.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah! O Sanji e o Usopp podem estar neles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:06.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O Mano Franky também!\N– O Mano Franky também!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:07.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso não é bom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:09.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desse jeito, vamos bater com certeza!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:11.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dona! Cadê o freio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:13.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu disse que não funciona, não disse?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:15.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês vão ter que se virar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:17.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos bater!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:21.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy! O que você vai fazer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:24.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou verificar lá dentro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:27.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:31.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Algo está voando...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:37.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que foi aquilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:38.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:40.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:50.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ai, ai, ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:52.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza! Consegui entrar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:55.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Q-Quem é você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:59.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oi! Sanji! Você está aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:02.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:07.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oi! Sanji! Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:08.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Talvez ali?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:16.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse cara... Será que é...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:19.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É o Chapéu de Palha Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:28.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:31.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você está aqui, Sanji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:35.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:36.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, cala a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:40.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,C-Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:42.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não há escapatória pra você!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:43.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cadê o Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:45.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Q-Quem é esse?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:47.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji! Ele é meu amigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:49.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não conhecemos ninguém assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:51.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.64,0:15:52.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então, falou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:56.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Atirem nele!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:02.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Chapéu de Palha está saindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:08.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele está dizendo que eles\Nnão estão aí... enquanto levam tiros!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:11.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então todo mundo ali dentro\Né funcionário do governo, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:14.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E daí se for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:17.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se não movermos esses vagões,\Nvamos sofrer muito dano também!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:27.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é um Sea Train, com certeza!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:28.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos ser derrubados!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:31.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pior, podemos todos explodir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:32.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parem!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:36.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É a hora da Família Franky brilhar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:38.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos demolir antes de bater!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:40.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza! Vamos dar uma mão também!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:43.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pessoal! É hora de trabalhar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:45.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:48.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:51.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Roronoa. Ele está te chamando.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:54.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Corte. Estão no caminho.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:56.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– "Tá"?!\N– "Tá"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:12.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O ego do mundo entrópico...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:15.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,pode ser cortado em pedaços.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:27.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)\t(2145,0,1,\c&H000000&)}Two-Sword Style Draw...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Rashomon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:40.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?!\N– O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:41.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?!\N– O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:46.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?!\N– O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:04.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:06.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Podiam ter {\i1}avisado{\i0} que iam fazer isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:08.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês ouviram eu dizer "Corte", não ouviram?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:10.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não achamos que ele realmente conseguiria!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.99,0:18:13.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Teríamos batido se\Nele não tivesse cortado, certo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:17.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É verdade, mas um aviso\Nteria sido legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.62,0:18:22.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você está me dizendo que um monstro\Ndesses nem é o capitão?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ainda não acabou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:29.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que diabos é aquilo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:31.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É um Sea King!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:34.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mais adiante neste trilho...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:36.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,está quem cortou aquela coisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:53.07,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Todos, voltem pros vagões da frente! É uma armadilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:54.28,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,– Uma armadilha?!\N– Uma armadilha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:56.45,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Que...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:02.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pensar que caí no plano do inimigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:04.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que erro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:05.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O maior erro da minha vida!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:11.17,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(2148,0,1,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Bom, então, cavalheiros! Boa viagem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:15.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Preciso alcançar o Sea Train!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.39,0:19:22.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se os criminosos que devemos escoltar\Nforem soltos no mundo de novo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:28.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,quanto sangue e quantas lágrimas\Nos civis terão que derramar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:35.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou mostrar que existe justiça\Nmesmo neste mundo injusto!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.49,0:19:41.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que meus braços e pernas sejam\Narrancados por essas ondas furiosas...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:46.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(3862,0,1,\c&H000000&)}Vou proteger\No futuro dos cidadãos inocentes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:21.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que é aquilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.50,0:20:27.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um Sea Train?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:32.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É um novo Sea Train?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:37.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tem algo ali!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:40.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã? O que é aquilo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:45.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uma pessoa? Tem alguém ali!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:50.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É o Cortador de Navios!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:51.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?!\N– O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:53.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– S-Sério?!\N– S-Sério?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Cortador de Navios?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:58.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É o T-Bone Cortador de Navios,\Num capitão do Quartel-General da Marinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:21:01.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele corta navios piratas como bifes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:02.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, é?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:03.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:07.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Incrível"?! Você está falando\Ncomo se fosse problema dos outros!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:09.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não podemos ficar parados assim.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, pessoal! Preparem-se pra atirar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:12.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:15.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:22.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esperem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:24.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que foi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.64,0:21:28.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É melhor corrermos ou ele vai cortar o {\i1}Rocketman{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:30.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês não estavam vendo antes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:32.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deixem com o Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:33.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não interfiram!
Comment: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:34.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.28,0:21:38.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou dizer só uma vez!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.94,0:21:40.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Saiam do nosso caminho!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.49,0:21:47.62,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Os vagões dos meus subordinados estavam no mesmo trilho,\Nentão não poderiam ter simplesmente passado por eles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.62,0:21:50.12,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,O que essas pessoas fizeram com meus homens?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.96,0:21:53.08,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Devem ser os companheiros da Nico Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.63,0:21:56.96,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,o que significa que aquele espadachim\Né o Caçador de Piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:22:01.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Este caminho leva à sede da justiça!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.97,0:22:06.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sou um capitão do Quartel-General da Marinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:08.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não vou viver em desgraça!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.31,0:22:11.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou parar vocês, bandidos, cortando-os ao meio!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:13.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não posso permitir isso...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:18.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,pois nosso destino está\Nalém de onde você está!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.61,0:22:22.32,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse cara é forte!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.53,0:22:25.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Venham!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.00,0:22:36.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Detesto esgrima torta!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.38,0:22:38.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Right-Angle Flying Bird:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.55,0:22:39.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Three-Sword Style:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:41.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Bull Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.47,0:22:47.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Bone...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.60,0:22:49.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.03,0:23:07.53,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele percebeu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.87,0:23:09.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Courageous Talons!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.05,0:23:26.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele derrotou o Cortador de Navios!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.68,0:23:34.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pensar que ele seguiu o Sea Train\Ndos vagões desconectados nesta tempestade...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.23,0:23:35.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que admirável!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:38.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas não podemos parar aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.86,0:23:45.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tenho certeza que o fardo da sua justiça é pesado,\Nmas nós também carregamos o nosso.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.20,0:23:52.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rápido! Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.95,0:23:56.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Capitão T-Bone pulou no mar! Ele está em perigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.33,0:23:59.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele pode ter sido atingido por aquele Sea Train.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.38,0:24:02.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cuide da língua, Marinheiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.38,0:24:05.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Saiba que nosso capitão\Ncortaria aquele trem ao meio!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.26,0:24:15.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A-Ah é?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.52,0:24:20.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo! Tenho certeza que foram o Sanji e\Nos outros que desconectaram aquele Sea Train.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.15,0:24:22.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então vamos alcançá-los logo?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.52,0:24:23.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Provavelmente.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.57,0:24:25.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza! Estamos chegando perto do inimigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.61,0:24:27.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.74,0:24:33.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vai, {\i1}Rocketman{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.70,0:24:36.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos acabar com aquele idiota do pombo!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=17}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=18}============================SIGNS AND TITLE=========================
